channel.title: G! Turbo - Game Over - The Cult, The Cowardly King and The Fool win!
channel.description:
# G! Turbo! - Wazza Edition
### Due to not enough classes yet. The thread for GI turbo is not yet being used. [Grand Idea FoL - Turbo Edition ](https://forum.imperium42.com/t/grand-idea-fol-turbo-edition/75468/11).
# Average Rules.
* Game starts at [date=2019-04-05 time=21:30:00 timezone="Europe/London"] * Days are 15 minutes. Twilight is 2 minutes. Nights are 5 minutes, unless I’m a failure and extend it. * Early day actions will be processed during the day, late day actions will be processed during Twilight, due to me being a failure once more. * There can be more than one King, but only a King election will take place once there are no Kings remaining. * I’m on PC, so don’t have mercy, feel free to make me want to die. * The amount of players are infinite but there must be at least 7 players.
1. Priestess 2. GamerPoke 3. Kape 4. Meteoro 5. BlueStorm 7. ~~Solic~~ - Abusive Dad 8. Hjasik 8. Squid 9. Isaac 10. ~~Grenade~~ - Mastermind # There is no line for classes until the game begins.
Classes will be watered down if they are not able to be used in Turbo, if classes can not work in turbo situations like this, they will be re-rolled.
